{"id":2354,"date":"2025-04-10T03:26:25","date_gmt":"2025-04-10T03:26:25","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/?p=2354"},"modified":"2025-04-11T04:27:12","modified_gmt":"2025-04-11T04:27:12","slug":"cuoc-thi-ve-tranh-voi-chu-de-chim-di-cu-va-vung-dat-ngap-nuoc","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/vi\/cuoc-thi-ve-tranh-voi-chu-de-chim-di-cu-va-vung-dat-ngap-nuoc\/","title":{"rendered":"CU\u1ed8C THI V\u1ebc TRANH V\u1edaI CH\u1ee6 \u0110\u1ec0 \u201cCHIM DI C\u01af V\u00c0 V\u00d9NG \u0110\u1ea4T NG\u1eacP N\u01af\u1edaC"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a d\u1ef1 \u00e1n \u201cT\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ef1c thi ph\u00e1p lu\u1eadt v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng cao nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 chim r\u1ebd m\u1ecf th\u00eca v\u00e0 c\u00e1c lo\u00e0i chim di c\u01b0 t\u1ea1i Khu D\u1ef1 tr\u1eef Sinh quy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ed3ng b\u1eb1ng s\u00f4ng H\u1ed3ng\u201d, cu\u1ed9c thi v\u1ebd tranh v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 <strong><em>\u201cChim di c\u01b0 v\u00e0 v\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea5t ng\u1eadp n\u01b0\u1edbc\u201d<\/em><\/strong> \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i 06 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc \u1edf ba t\u1ec9nh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, Ninh B\u00ecnh v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh. Nh\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1eddng tham gia bao g\u1ed3m: Tr\u01b0\u1eddng THCS Ho\u00e0nh S\u01a1n (Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh), Tr\u01b0\u1eddng THCS Y\u00ean Th\u1eafng, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng THCS Y\u00ean \u0110\u1ed3ng (Ninh B\u00ecnh), v\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng THCS Nam Th\u1ecbnh, THCS 14-10, THCS Th\u1ee5y Xu\u00e2n (Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh).<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-2358\" src=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/QNT08992-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/QNT08992-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/QNT08992-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/QNT08992-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/QNT08992-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/QNT08992-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-2357\" src=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/QNT08990-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/QNT08990-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/QNT08990-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/QNT08990-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/QNT08990-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/QNT08990-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-2356\" src=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/QNT08991-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/QNT08991-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/QNT08991-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/QNT08991-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/QNT08991-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/QNT08991-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-2355\" src=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/QNT08985-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/QNT08985-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/QNT08985-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/QNT08985-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/QNT08985-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/QNT08985-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Cu\u1ed9c thi \u0111\u00e3 thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 tham gia nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh t\u1eeb h\u01a1n 60 b\u00e0i d\u1ef1 thi c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. C\u00e1c t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o m\u00e0 c\u00f2n truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 chim di c\u01b0, ng\u1eebng s\u0103n b\u1eafn v\u00e0 ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 tr\u00e1i ph\u00e9p c\u00e1c lo\u00e0i chim, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u00e1c v\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea5t ng\u1eadp n\u01b0\u1edbc, l\u00e0 n\u01a1i tr\u00fa ng\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng lo\u00e0i chim n\u00e0y. Cu\u1ed9c thi c\u0169ng g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n n\u00e2ng cao nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n c\u00e1c lo\u00e0i chim di c\u01b0 v\u00e0 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang.<\/p>\n<p>Sau qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn, 06 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 nh\u00f3m h\u1ecdc sinh \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb WildAct. C\u00e1c t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c m\u00e0 c\u00f2n mang \u0111\u1eadm gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb nh\u00e2n v\u0103n, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m v\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c lo\u00e0i chim di c\u01b0.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-2359\" src=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/z6252142851186_521451e5fcd0c9b48af9edff65a0216c-1-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/z6252142851186_521451e5fcd0c9b48af9edff65a0216c-1-225x300.jpg 225w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/z6252142851186_521451e5fcd0c9b48af9edff65a0216c-1-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/z6252142851186_521451e5fcd0c9b48af9edff65a0216c-1-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/z6252142851186_521451e5fcd0c9b48af9edff65a0216c-1-1536x2048.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/z6252142851186_521451e5fcd0c9b48af9edff65a0216c-1.jpg 1836w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-2361\" src=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/z6249154045070_4e18fb30f7578481c0c4765cf8ff014b-291x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"291\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/z6249154045070_4e18fb30f7578481c0c4765cf8ff014b-291x300.jpg 291w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/z6249154045070_4e18fb30f7578481c0c4765cf8ff014b-992x1024.jpg 992w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/z6249154045070_4e18fb30f7578481c0c4765cf8ff014b-768x793.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/z6249154045070_4e18fb30f7578481c0c4765cf8ff014b-1488x1536.jpg 1488w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/z6249154045070_4e18fb30f7578481c0c4765cf8ff014b-1984x2048.jpg 1984w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 291px) 100vw, 291px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, cu\u1ed9c thi c\u0169ng g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n n\u00e2ng cao nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh v\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y \u00fd th\u1ee9c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u00e1c lo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt hoang d\u00e3 n\u00f3i chung, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ed1ng b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng cho th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a d\u1ef1 \u00e1n \u201cT\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ef1c thi ph\u00e1p lu\u1eadt v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng cao nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 chim r\u1ebd m\u1ecf th\u00eca v\u00e0 c\u00e1c lo\u00e0i chim di c\u01b0 t\u1ea1i Khu D\u1ef1 tr\u1eef Sinh quy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ed3ng b\u1eb1ng s\u00f4ng H\u1ed3ng\u201d, cu\u1ed9c thi v\u1ebd tranh v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 \u201cChim di c\u01b0 v\u00e0&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2355,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[43],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-2354","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-moi-nhat"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2354","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddabl